tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE LandUsePatterns (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    area_name VARCHAR(256),
    land_type VARCHAR(128),
    land_area DECIMAL(10, 2),
    green_space_potential BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE Land_Use_Patterns (
    area_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    area_name VARCHAR(50),
    land_use_type VARCHAR(50),
    land_area DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE Green_Space_Expansion (
    green_space_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    area_id INT,
    green_space_name VARCHAR(50),
    green_space_area DECIMAL,
    CONSTRAINT fk_area_id FOREIGN KEY (area_id) REFERENCES Land_Use_Patterns(area_id)
)

CREATE TABLE User_Reviews (
    review_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    green_space_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    review_text TEXT,
    rating INT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_green_space_id FOREIGN KEY (green_space_id) REFERENCES Green_Space_Expansion(green_space_id)
)

CREATE TABLE Area_Details (
    details_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    area_id INT,
    population INT,
    facilities VARCHAR(100),
    CONSTRAINT fk_area_id FOREIGN KEY (area_id) REFERENCES Land_Use_Patterns(area_id)
)

CREATE TABLE land_use_patterns (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    area_name VARCHAR(255),
    land_type VARCHAR(255),
    area_size INT,
    green_space_potential BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE green_spaces (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    space_name VARCHAR(255),
    location VARCHAR(255),
    size INT,
    facilities VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE land_owners (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    owner_name VARCHAR(255),
    contact_info VARCHAR(255),
    land_area_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE land_area_details (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    area_id INT,
    boundary_polygon GEOGRAPHY,
    development_status VARCHAR(255),
    zoning VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE survey_results (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    surveyor_name VARCHAR(255),
    survey_date DATE,
    area_id INT,
    comments TEXT
)
